{"tid":700772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★蘋果iOS又出事 升級最新版本電量急跌30%","createTime":"2018-06-13T15:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T05:35:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0d3c26140ec10539bd2f3d2a687a60c46694dd34","tid":700772,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】蘋果手機作業系統月初推出升級至iOS 11.4，有iPhone用戶投訴更新分鐘後iPhone電量插水式下跌，由50%跌至20%。有科技網站指，所有iPhone型號在更新後也有類似問題，有網民指自行「降級」至11.3.1，耗電問題才解決。<br />\n<br />\n據科技網站Softpedia報道，不少用戶稱其iPhone在升級到iOS 11.4後，電池消耗速度反而大幅度加快。有用戶指，其iPhone 6s Plus遇到相似問題，手機更新後並在不使用的情況下，手機電量從幾分鐘從50%降至20%。<br />\n<br />\n亦有用戶指，其iPhone 6s在更新到iOS 11.4後也遇到同樣問題，當手機充電至100%，並重新啟動，然後等待四小時，電池電量降到40％，而在更新後三天，問題仍然無改善。<br />\n<br />\n官方目前未有解決方案，有用戶聲稱自行將手機「降級」至11.3.1，耗電問題才解決。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9Cios%E5%8F%88%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E9%9B%BB%E9%87%8F%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C30-044400137.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259Cios%25E5%258F%2588%25E5%2587%25BA%25E4%25BA%258B-%25E5%258D%2587%25E7%25B4%259A%25E6%259C%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2589%2588%25E6%259C%25AC%25E9%259B%25BB%25E9%2587%258F%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B7%258C30-044400137.html&d=RaTtOC72cGBplrU6jogn30%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=7bd11ef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9Cios%E5%8F%88%E5%87%BA%E4%BA%8B-%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E9%9B%BB%E9%87%8F%E6%80%A5%E8%B7%8C30-044400137.html</a>"},{"pid":"4399fe1f065e52a5008a59ef990a3c6f7966b937","tid":700772,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy"